  <summary date="2019-08-29T21:19:31Z" status="Introduced in House">VA Medical Center Improvement Act

This bill directs the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to require each director of a VA medical facility to submit a plan to improve such facility in such a fashion as would result in the facility obtaining a VA five-star rating.</summary>
